  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Clickable, Dragable, KeyedComponent, Scrollable, Visible, java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class FullFunctionPane
extends ScrollablePane
implements KeyedComponent, java.awt.event.KeyListener, Dragable, java.lang.Runnable
    This class is like a FullFunctionScreen but a "subscreen" version. In other words, it is not a FocusManager and there can be multiple instances on one single screen
